      "writtenOn": "2020-01-08T14:44:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As described down below, in my response to your comment, this method is where we do a lazy copy of the pixels, so that\u0027s why you can safely use kNever_SkCopyPixelsMode.",
